lass=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ganarajsavant\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9e2ba156ceef8251448adf78f81cebff?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9e2ba156ceef8251448adf78f81cebff?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ganarajsavant\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Ganaraj Savant <small>(ganarajsavant)</small></a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">7 stycznia, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Optimized my site better (I was able to find the difference) and was able to resolve the issue caused by the \"Lazyload\" feature of other plgins.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Free for all!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/emanuel-pietri\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2b6d0fd0a026a1c88b2dc9eb821f0043?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2b6d0fd0a026a1c88b2dc9eb821f0043?s=3