				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fascinating</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fedibelkacem\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c128a4f9e3d59cf7eb2a8f0555f64ce3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c128a4f9e3d59cf7eb2a8f0555f64ce3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/fedibelkacem\" class=\"reviewer-name\">fedibelkacem</a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">15 stycznia, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The Otter blocks plugin helped me to understand how beautiful templates are designed. Thanks to the developers.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Saves you time and adds powerful blocks</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bruceholland\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5df792ba656666419c730062f6a699b2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5df792ba656666419c730062f6a699b2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bruceholland\" class=\"reviewer-name\">BruceHolland</a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">30 grudnia, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Making great pages is easier with Otter\'s blocks.  Thank you for sharing your expertise.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Otter replaced 3 plugins</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brfagaten\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/caa2ad3fadd896f86aea3d8a9b4efa74?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/caa2ad3fadd896f86aea3d8a9b4efa74?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/brfagaten\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Tomas Åberg <small>(brfagaten)</small></a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">27 grudnia, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I was looking for a simple plugin that could add some extra blocks in Guthenberg. \nMy criteria was that it should feel like vanilla WordPress, I shouldn\'t have to go in to different menus and settings just to add a simple something. \n\nNot only did Otter check all my criterias it delivers so much more!\nThe section block did a great lift of my start page.\n\nThis plugin made it possible for me to replace three other plugins that:\n1. Created a kinda good looking gallery\n2. A pricing list\n3. Feature list </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">super!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/amandutxi\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ad7ea33db672c283463113627507ca9b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ad7ea33db672c283463113627507ca9b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/amandutxi\" class=\"reviewer-name\">amandutxi</a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">25 listopada, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">make my work easier</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Left over folder after deletion</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nickster72\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/93df7a1edf351a1220c7013a3a0be660?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/93df7a1edf351a1220c7013a3a0be660?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nickster72\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nickster72</a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">19 listopada, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hello,\nI need to do a fresh install of this plugin.\nWhen I deleted the plugin I want to make sure everything is gone before reinstall.\nCan you confirm with me that the folder called slider2 with about 6 jpegs called freelayerslider under wp-content/uploads belongs to this plugin.\n\nAlso would like to know if the folder themeisle-gutenberg also belongs to this plugin?\n\nThank you. Let me know.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Useful Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mahrus21\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/334d3d9b508eaba4edfa5f2e803e09a1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/334d3d9b508eaba4edfa5f2e803e09a1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mahrus21\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mahrus21</a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">11 listopada, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Thank you so much</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Buen complemento</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/whomples\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b12544f03e03afe0305ffdb33fc4dc66?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b12544f03e03afe0305ffdb33fc4dc66?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/whomples\" class=\"reviewer-name\">whomples</a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">13 października, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Unos cuantos bloques para Gutenberg muy útiles y con posibilidades, unido a su gratuidad le hacen un complemento magnífico.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">very nice plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aajsl28\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b9a2389d1d436b750623b740be4a20e6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b9a2389d1d436b750623b740be4a20e6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aajsl28\" class=\"reviewer-name\">aajsl28</a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">13 września, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Smart and neat design, very useful and easy to arrange in my website. Thanks!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect companion and