, so your design process is backed up, every step of the way.\"></a><p><strong>Revision History.</strong> Switch between earlier versions of your page design, so your design process is backed up, every step of the way.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-7.gif?rev=1608748\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-7.gif?rev=1608748\" alt=\"&lt;strong&gt;Shape Divider.&lt;/strong&gt; Choose from a wide array of shape dividers and separate your sections in endless ways, that until now were simply not possible.\"></a><p><strong>Shape Divider.</strong> Choose from a wide array of shape dividers and separate your sections in endless ways, that until now were simply not possible.</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:14351:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Write off money without permission</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aulanov\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/59d26e04ee1b33d115f67eadab5e7469?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/59d26e04ee1b33d115f67eadab5e7469?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aulanov\" class=\"reviewer-name\">aulanov</a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">20 stycznia, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I bought this plugin in 2020. Yesterday, without my explicit consent, the renewal fee was surreptitiously charged automatically for the renewal of the license, which I do not need. I did not give my consent to the payment number # 9907810, and I did not check any boxes in my personal account. I believe that the money was actually stolen. I advise no one to buy this plugin, as you will also be secretly debited money from your account. Technical support does not respond, they do not want to return the money. This is an outrage.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best Page Builder</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/johns1951\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/949c8f391e645ddb5c98f0c15f95e72a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/949c8f391e645ddb5c98f0c15f95e72a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/johns1951\" class=\"reviewer-name\">johns1951</a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">19 stycznia, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have been using Elementor for over a year.  It was tons of features and is very reliable.  I also use the Pro version.  You will not find a better page builder with ease of use and great features.  There are lots of other plugins made foe Elementor that add just about any feature you may need.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">easy to use, wp-beginners approved</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 z 5 gwiazdek\" data-title-template=\"%s z 5 gwiazdek\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Przez <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mohnster\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/342c2e7aa9d383ba1037baea0c08f819?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/342c2e7aa9d383ba1037baea0c08f819?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mohnster\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mohnster</a> dnia <span class=\"review-date\">18 stycznia, 2021</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'m an absolutely beginner in wordpress and used this plugin for building my first website in self-study (did it because nobody in my company was able to create a company-website) ... and the result is: I\'m totally fascinated of how intuitive the Elementor plugin helps me building a website. Big thanks to the author!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-